script: Total darkness. A faint wind sound.
Spotlight reveals Devi mid-air, holding a closed black umbrella, calm and powerful.
Devi descends slowly from an industrial ladder, solid and realistic.
She steps firmly onto the runway floor.
Devi opens the large black umbrella. Rain falls only around her.
hook: Witness the power of atmosphere in fashion.
